Class ContestantInformation

java.lang.Object
  aslam.ContestantInformation

public class ContestantInformation
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds the information of a contestant. It has fields for first name, last name, street address, city, province, postal code, phone number and birth date.

Author:
Mohid Aslam September 21 2015
